This product, and the prebuilt release bundles, include third-party components:

1. Linux kernel ("resin")
   The guest kernel (assets/Image) is the Linux kernel, built from unmodified
   upstream source with the configuration in kernel/resin_defconfig.
   License: GPL-2.0-only.
   Source: https://cdn.kernel.org/pub/linux/kernel/ (version pinned in
   scripts/build-kernel.sh), plus kernel/resin_defconfig in this repository.

2. BusyBox
   The in-guest userland binary (assets/irx/bin/busybox), obtained from the
   Alpine Linux minirootfs.
   License: GPL-2.0-only.
   Source: https://busybox.net/ and https://gitlab.alpinelinux.org/alpine/aports.

3. musl libc
   The dynamic loader (assets/irx/lib/ld-musl-aarch64.so.1), obtained from the
   Alpine Linux minirootfs.
   License: MIT.
   Source: https://musl.libc.org/ and https://gitlab.alpinelinux.org/alpine/aports.

